OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773857158
OL,3,CDrug dealer whose own CCTV caught him
OL,4,Csinging about 'dirty cash' is jailed
OL,6,FA drug dealer whose own CCTV caught
OL,7,Fhim singing about 'dirty cash' while
OL,8,Fhandling illicit money has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor 15 years along with others.
OL,11,FBertie Payne coordinated the supply of
OL,12,Fclass A drugs across east Kent and
OL,13,Fused a luxury watch business as a
OL,14,Fcover up, allowing him to fake
OL,15,Finvoices in order to run large amounts
OL,16,Fof money through the accounts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773857158
OL,3,CDrug dealer whose own CCTV caught him
OL,4,Csinging about 'dirty cash' is jailed
OL,6,FThe 30 year old led a group of seven
OL,7,Fmen to supply and distribute 24kg of
OL,8,Fcocaine, 10kg of ketamine and 5,000
OL,9,Fecstasy tablets across east Kent
OL,10,Fbetween August 2024 and January 2025.
OL,12,FFollowing an investigation by officers
OL,13,Ffrom the Kent and Essex Serious Crime
OL,14,FDirectorate, Payne, of Plumstone Road,
OL,15,FAcol, Birchington, was arrested in a
OL,16,Fcar park in Bluewater on Friday 24
OL,17,FJanuary 2025 as he was about to hand
OL,18,Fanother man, Halim Lashi, #50,000 in
OL,19,Fcash.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773857158
OL,3,CDrug dealer whose own CCTV caught him
OL,4,Csinging about 'dirty cash' is jailed
OL,6,FBoth were also wearing luxury watches
OL,7,Fand had more watches inside their
OL,8,Fvehicles. They were each arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of money laundering offences
OL,10,Fand police began collating evidence.
OL,12,FAs part of this, CCTV was recovered
OL,13,Ffrom the office Payne used for the
OL,14,Fwatch business.
OL,16,FWhile reviewing this footage police
OL,17,Ffound him counting large amounts of
OL,18,Fmoney and he was also heard to sing
OL,19,Fthe song 'Dirty Cash'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773857158
OL,3,CDrug dealer whose own CCTV caught him
OL,4,Csinging about 'dirty cash' is jailed
OL,6,FMore than 2,100 text messages were
OL,7,Ffound to have been sent by Payne and
OL,8,F'PBoss', later identified as 51 year
OL,9,Fold Peter Nicholls, who officers
OL,10,Farrested on Thursday 3 April 2025.
OL,12,FPolice concluded that Nicholls was
OL,13,FPayne's right-hand man and that he
OL,14,Fworked with several others to move
OL,15,Fclass A and B drugs all around east
OL,16,FKent. Lashi, Payne and Nicholls also
OL,17,Fhad dealings with moving the illicit
OL,18,Fmoney, which included the use of
OL,19,Fcrypto currency.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773857158
OL,3,CDrug dealer whose own CCTV caught him
OL,4,Csinging about 'dirty cash' is jailed
OL,6,FNicholls, of Ellington Road, Ramsgate,
OL,7,Fwas also found to have used the home
OL,8,Faddress of Karen Gordon, to store some
OL,9,Fof the drugs before they were moved
OL,10,Fon. She was later arrested.
OL,12,FFollowing the comprehensive
OL,13,Finvestigation officers additionally
OL,14,Farrested Massimo Fierro, Harry
OL,15,FHathaway, Mitchell Laing, Reece
OL,16,FStovell and Klein Taylor. Along with
OL,17,FPayne and Nicholls, they were all
OL,18,Fcharged with conspiracy to supply
OL,19,Fcocaine.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773857158
OL,3,CDrug dealer whose own CCTV caught him
OL,4,Csinging about 'dirty cash' is jailed
OL,6,FPayne and Nicholls were additionally
OL,7,Fcharged with conspiracy to supply
OL,8,Fecstasy, and along with Fierro all
OL,9,Fthree were charged with conspiracy to
OL,10,Fsupply ketamine.
OL,12,FPayne and Nicholls were additionally
OL,13,Fcharged with money laundering
OL,14,Foffences, along with Lashi.
OL,16,FEach of the defendants admitted their
OL,17,Fcharges apart from Lashi, who denied
OL,18,Fthe charge of money laundering. He was
OL,19,Ffound guilty at a previous trial in
OL,20,FOctober 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773857158
OL,3,CDrug dealer whose own CCTV caught him
OL,4,Csinging about 'dirty cash' is jailed
OL,6,FLashi, 31, of Lynwood Gardens,
OL,7,FCroydon, was given a two year
OL,8,Fsuspended sentence while Karen Gordon,
OL,9,F52, of Ellington Road, Ramsgate, was
OL,10,Fsentenced to four years and three
OL,11,Fmonths in jail.
OL,13,FThe rest of the group were sentenced
OL,14,Fas follows on Monday 16 March.
OL,16,FPayne, Nicholls, Gordon and Lashi were
OL,17,Fsentenced at Maidstone Crown Court on
OL,18,FThursday 12 March.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773857158
OL,3,CDrug dealer whose own CCTV caught him
OL,4,Csinging about 'dirty cash' is jailed
OL,6,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Martin Lacey said: "Payne
OL,8,Fwent to great lengths to conceal his
OL,9,Fcriminality by not only running the
OL,10,Fmoney through what appeared to be a
OL,11,Flegitimate business, but he also
OL,12,Frecruited others to handle the drugs
OL,13,Fin an effort to distance himself from
OL,14,Fthe criminality.
OL,16,F"This was a large-scale operation
OL,17,Fwhich saw over #800,000 of drugs being
OL,18,Fdistributed and supplied throughout
OL,19,Feast Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773857158
OL,3,CDrug dealer whose own CCTV caught him
OL,4,Csinging about 'dirty cash' is jailed
OL,6,F"Many vulnerable drug users were
OL,7,Ftargeted which not only affects their
OL,8,Flives but that of their family, and
OL,9,Fblights local communities.
OL,11,F"Payne thought his operation was
OL,12,Fsophisticated and that he wouldn't get
OL,13,Ffound out but his sentencing shows
OL,14,Fthat crime doesn't pay and that if you
OL,15,Fare involved in criminality you will
OL,16,Fbe caught and you will face the
OL,17,Fconsequences."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
